txt.en:
'In bat cave, I sometimes see white stuff on the ground. Know what I mean?'

You tell him you do, and that it is called 'guano.'

'Guano? What's that? Will you get some for me?'
Viznak can be found outside of Seregost once you have completed Surveying Seregost.\n\nYou should talk to Viznak.

'So this is guano? Smells good! Want to taste?'

You vigorously shake your head no. Viznak shrugs and then gives it a try.

'So tasty! Maybe I should get my own bats!'

'In bat cave, I sometimes see white stuff on the ground. Know what I mean?'

You tell him you do, and that it is called 'guano.'

'Guano? What's that? Will you get some for me?'
TBD Go to Agarnaith Ranger Camp
Viznak has asked you to collect some guano for him from the Gloom-lord's lair. You shudder to think why he wants it.
Talk to Viznak after completing Surveying Seregost
Guano piles can be found in the Lair of the Gloom-lord.\n\nYou should collect guano piles because Viznak asked.
